Print all the existing years in LIS for a given country.

Source: R/countries_and_years.R
show_country_years_lis.Rd

Print all the existing years in LIS for a given country.

Usage

show_country_years_lis(iso2 = NULL)

Arguments

iso2

A string with 2 characters, specifically an iso2 code present in show_countries_lis().

Value

A numeric vector.

Examples

show_country_years_lis("it")
#>  [1] 1977 1978 1979 1980 1981 1982 1983 1984 1986 1987 1989 1991 1993 1995 1998
#> [16] 2000 2002 2004 2006 2008 2010 2012 2014 2016 2020
show_country_years_lis("us")
#>  [1] 1963 1964 1965 1966 1967 1968 1969 1970 1971 1972 1973 1974 1975 1976 1977
#> [16] 1978 1979 1980 1981 1982 1983 1984 1985 1986 1987 1988 1989 1990 1991 1992
#> [31] 1993 1994 1995 1996 1997 1998 1999 2000 2001 2002 2003 2004 2005 2006 2007
#> [46] 2008 2009 2010 2011 2012 2013 2014 2015 2016 2017 2018 2019 2020 2021 2022
#> [61] 2023
